        "title": "Benefits of a Hosted Shopping Cart Solution",
        "style": "light",
        "decorator": "none",
        "content": "<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<p><strong>Customer Support.</strong> Hosted shopping carts provide a top-notch level of customer support and always take care of the server side of things, allowing you to focus directly on achieving your business goals.</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p><strong>Easy to Personalize.&nbsp;</strong>Quickly pick a design for your hosted shopping cart&nbsp;by choosing from dozens of templates available. You can style and personalize it however you want in a minimal amount of time, making them a great solution for up and coming businesses. The work is in adding your products to the site, uploading images, selecting payment and shipment options as well as making sure that your website is rich with compelling content.</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p><strong>Affordable.&nbsp;</strong>No need to overpay for your server &ndash; you can pay just a monthly subscription fee for the time you want your website running. The monthly fee includes hosting, access to your admin&#39;s panel and 24/7 customer service.</p>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n",
