    {
        "id": 5,
        "type": "two-columns-text",
        "name": "Text",
        "title": "Universal Features Offered by Hosted Shopping Carts",
        "style": "dark",
        "contentBefore": "<p style=\"text-align:center\">Now that we have determined the benefits of using hosted shopping carts for growing your business, look at some of the core features that will allow you to sell your products on the Internet successfully.</p>\n",
        "items": [
            {
                "text": "<ul>\n\t<li><strong>Functional Product Images</strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>It is a &quot;must have&quot; for a hosted shopping cart integration to allow you to upload high-resolution product images, as it is customers&#39; only opportunity to see the product and be impressed by it. Another key item is the ability to resize pictures to your needs since the bigger (and the clearer) the image is the better. Look for carts that give you the opportunity to zoom in on products.</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><strong>Easy Navigation</strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Take care of your customers by offering them streamlined navigation. Include some filtering options, so they can find exactly what they want. Make sure that the hosted shopping cart provider will provide it for you by specifying that you need it to be data-driven and programmatic.</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><strong>Deals and Discounts</strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Deal shoppers love to use their coupons. With multiple services that can provide coupons, your website needs to be able to receive them and promote special deals which are key in driving campaign ROI.</p>\n"
            },
            {
                "text": "<ul>\n\t<li><strong>Product Reviews</strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Product reviews have shown their beneficial influence on conversion rates as research suggests that more than 70% of internet buyers trust product reviews posted online.&nbsp;<strong>Reviews help customers make product choices and convert them. In order to capitalize on the power of customer reviews,</strong>&nbsp;you have to look for a hosted shopping cart&nbsp;<a href=\"https://virtocommerce.com/glossary/best-ecommerce-platforms\">platform</a>&nbsp;that allows you to include product reviews or has a way to implement third-party product reviews.</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><strong>Fast &amp; Easy Checkout</strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Checkout is the final moment of the purchase and you, as the owner have to go out of your way to make the checkout process painless to your customer. Remember that clients always look for the shortest line and want to complete the final steps as fast as possible. To do that, you need to ensure that your checkout form has very few fields and is located on a single page. By doing this, you will promote the user-friendliness of the website and allow for better conversion rates.</p>\n"
            }
        ],
